text: "Paperback Writer" is a 1966 song by The Beatles and was released A-side to their eleventh single Rain. It went to number 1 in the United Kingdom, the United States, Australia, Canada, Germany, Ireland, New Zealand, the Netherlands, Norway and Sweden. == References == Category:1966 songs Category:The Beatles songs Category:Hard rock songs Category:Psychedelic rock songs
title: Paperback Writer
